metadata.name: Early Colony II
metadata.description:
"Early Colony II" is a follow up scene to my genesis NFT "Early Colony" which was minted on Rarible 28/03/2021 https://rarible.com/token/0xd07dc4262bcdbf85190c01c996b4c06a461d2430:398631

Early Colony II is set in a future Mars colony featuring Chi #093, Satoshi #28, Nasir #087, Claire #047, and Mark #072, from "Tyrone Layne's Human Database" https://opensea.io/collection/humandatabase

It also features the iconic XCOPY "Right-click and Save As Guy" NFT.

@tyronelayne
